      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for someone who prioritizes function over aesthetics. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, a few minor dings, and some clear coat fading on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and visible wear on the driver's seat, though all essential electronics and climate controls remain fully operational. Mechanically, it starts consistently and runs well, though it may require some routine suspension work in the near future. It\u2019s an honest, high-mileage car that still has plenty of life left for the right owner.",
